track_notes: The route leads from the layby on the A66 at Scales. Distance 11.1 miles / 17.86 Km with 3300 ft / 1006m ascent. Wainwrights Mungrisdale Common, Bowscale Fell and Bannerdale Vrags also visited. More info at www.wainwrightsontheairblogspot.co.uk
